channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Oregon Ducks Unveil Black “Generation O” Football Uniforms
item.description: Oregon unveiled the first combination of its new “Generation O” uniforms on Wednesday afternoon with an all-black option that blends various elements from the Ducks’ previous designs.

item.title: Ole Miss Rebels Unveil Powder Blue-Accented Road Jersey
item.description: Ole Miss unveiled the first powder blue-accented road jersey in school history on Monday morning, granting the wishes of a large portion of the Rebels' fanbase.
